OL,3,CConstance Marten and Mark Gordon
OL,4,Cconvicted over death of their newborn
OL,5,Cbaby
OL,7,FConstance Marten and her partner Mark
OL,8,FGordon have been convicted of the
OL,9,Fgross negligence manslaughter of their
OL,10,Fnewborn baby.
OL,12,FMarten, 38, and Gordon, 51, went on
OL,13,Fthe run with daughter Victoria in
OL,14,Fearly 2023 after their four other
OL,15,Fchildren were taken into care.
OL,17,FPolice had launched a nationwide hunt
OL,18,Fafter their car burst into flames on
OL,19,Fthe motorway near Bolton, Greater
OL,20,FManchester.
