OL,7,FThe couple travelled across England
OL,8,Fand went off-grid, sleeping in a tent
OL,9,Fon the South Downs where baby Victoria
OL,10,Fdied.
OL,12,FAfter seven weeks on the run, the
OL,13,Fdefendants were arrested in Brighton,
OL,14,FEast Sussex.
OL,16,FFollowing a desperate search, police
OL,17,Ffound their baby dead amid rubbish
OL,18,Finside a Lidl bag in a disused shed
OL,19,Fnearby.
