OL,7,FVictoria's remains were too badly
OL,8,Fdecomposed to establish the cause of
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said she died from
OL,12,Fhypothermia in the cold and damp
OL,13,Fconditions inside the flimsy tent or
OL,14,Fwas smothered.
OL,16,FThe defendants claimed their
OL,17,Fdaughter's death was a tragic accident
OL,18,Fafter Marten fell asleep on her.
