OL,7,FA jury in their retrial found Marten
OL,8,Fand Gordon unanimously guilty of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter on Monday.
OL,11,FIn their first trial last year, the
OL,12,Fdefendants were convicted of
OL,13,Fperverting the course of justice,
OL,14,Fconcealing the birth of a child and
OL,15,Fchild cruelty.
OL,17,FDetective Superintendent Lewis Basford
OL,18,Fof Scotland Yard, said: "Today, the
OL,19,Fjustice we have long fought for has
OL,20,Fbeen finally been served for baby
OL,21,FVictoria.
