OL,7,F"The selfish actions of Mark Gordon
OL,8,Fand Constance Marten resulted in the
OL,9,Fdeath of a newborn baby who should
OL,10,Fhave had the rest of her life ahead of
OL,11,Fher."
OL,13,FThe senior officer said Victoria's
OL,14,Fdeath was "completely avoidable" as
OL,15,Fthe defendant had plenty of
OL,16,Fopportunities to "do the right thing"
OL,17,Fand ask for help.
