OL,7,FIn light of the conviction, the family
OL,8,Fcourt decision to take Marten's four
OL,9,Fother children into care was "shown to
OL,10,Fbe right", he said.
OL,12,FWhen Marten became pregnant for a
OL,13,Ffifth time, she kept it secret, giving
OL,14,Fbirth in a hired holiday cottage on
OL,15,FChristmas Eve 2022.
OL,17,FThe defendants' attempts to keep baby
OL,18,FVictoria under wraps prompted the
OL,19,Fmajor police alert after a placenta
OL,20,Fwas found inside their abandoned car
OL,21,Fnear Bolton on January 5 2023.
