OL,7,FThe defendants fled the scene with
OL,8,FVictoria, leaving behind the family
OL,9,Fcat named Sasha in a box, around
OL,10,F#2,000 in cash, 34 "burner" phones and
OL,11,Fother belongings.
OL,13,FThey spent hundreds of pounds on taxis
OL,14,Fto take them from the North West, to
OL,15,FHarwich in Essex, East Ham in London
OL,16,Fand on to Newhaven.
OL,18,FVictoria was only briefly glimpsed on
OL,19,FCCTV footage in London wearing the
OL,20,Fsame babygrow, later recovered with
OL,21,Fher body inside the Lidl bag.
