OL,7,FThe prosecution asserted that Victoria
OL,8,Fwas carried under Marten's jacket or
OL,9,Fin a Lidl bag without adequate
OL,10,Fclothing, warmth or shelter.
OL,12,FAfter she died, the defendants were
OL,13,Fcaught on CCTV scavenging in bins for
OL,14,Ffood even though Marten had received
OL,15,Fthousands of pounds from a trust fund
OL,16,Fand had #19,000 in the bank.
