OL,7,FThe defendants were arrested after
OL,8,Fbuying supplies in Brighton on
OL,9,FFebruary 27 2023, and refused to say
OL,10,Fwhere the baby was, with Gordon
OL,11,Fdeclaring: "What's the big deal?"
OL,13,FMore than 1,000 Metropolitan Police
OL,14,Fofficers searched for Victoria for two
OL,15,Fdays before she was discovered in an
OL,16,Fallotment shed wrapped in a pink sheet
OL,17,Fand hidden beneath dirt and rubbish in
OL,18,Fa Lidl bag.
