OL,7,FIn a police interview, Marten said: "I
OL,8,Fhad her in my jacket and I hadn't
OL,9,Fslept properly in quite a few days and
OL,10,Ferm, I fell asleep holding her sitting
OL,11,Fup and she, when I woke up, she wasn't
OL,12,Falive."
OL,14,FJurors were told Marten had been
OL,15,Fwarned by social workers about the
OL,16,Frisk of falling asleep with a baby
OL,17,Flying on her and that a tent was
OL,18,Funsuitable.
