OL,7,FBoth defendants gave evidence in their
OL,8,Fretrial, but each cut short their
OL,9,Ftestimony, with Marten, an aristocrat,
OL,10,Fdescribing the prosecution as
OL,11,F"heartless" and "diabolical".
OL,13,FJurors in the defendant's first trial
OL,14,Fin 2024 were not told about Gordon's
OL,15,Fviolent past, which was only partly
OL,16,Frevealed in their second trial.
