OL,7,FJurors in the retrial appeared visibly
OL,8,Fshaken by the revelations, even though
OL,9,FMarten had accidentally blurted out
OL,10,FGordon's rape conviction while giving
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FIn 2017, Gordon was convicted of
OL,14,Fassaulting two female police officers
OL,15,Fat a maternity unit in Wales where
OL,16,FMarten gave birth to their first child
OL,17,Funder a fake identity.
