OL,7,FJurors were not told that Gordon was
OL,8,Falso suspected of an incident of
OL,9,Fdomestic violence in 2019, which left
OL,10,FMarten with a shattered spleen.
OL,12,FGordon had refused to allow paramedics
OL,13,Finto their London flat to treat her,
OL,14,Feven though she was 14 weeks pregnant,
OL,15,Fit emerged during a legal argument.
OL,17,FShe spent eight days in hospital, then
OL,18,Fput her life and that of her unborn
OL,19,Fchild at risk by attempting to
OL,20,Fdischarge herself, with Gordon's
OL,21,Fsupport, it was alleged.
